quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  17,94,Quod prevented people ex believing when guidance advenit them their dictus est DEUS send human est messenger
  17,95,Dictus Si terra inhabited angels nos sent down them caelum angel messenger
  17,96,Dictus DEUS suffices prout testis me vos! He est fully Cognizant de His worshipers Seer
  17,97,Whomever DEUS guides the enim guided unus. Ac whomever He sends astray vos nunquam invenit them any dominus magister Eum. Nos summon them Feria Resurrection forcibly; blind dumb surdus! Their destination est Hell; whenever it cools nos increase their fire
  17,98,Such est their just retribution abinde they rejected noster revelations. They dictus Post nos turn into bones fragments nos resurrected new creation
  17,99,they non vide DEUS created caelum terra est able to create same creations? (Ut) He predetermined them irrevocable vita span disbelievers insist upon disbelieving
  17,100,Proclaim Si vos possessed my Dominus treasures mercy vos withheld them fearing vos exhaust them! human est est stingy